snippet.title: Players fend off the first Emperor Invasion | Guilds of Gods
snippet.description:
Twelve hours prior, players received word that the emperor was preparing to invade. Players readied themselves for the biggest challenge yet - a fight with the emperor himself.

-----------------------------------------------------------

Guilds of Gods is a sandbox MMO about building your name through wealth and glory. Explore Eloria, refine the land, build your party and conquer!

Play Now at https://guildsofgods.com/play
